install guest addition

In Virtual Box Manager
  Devices -> Install Guest Additions 

in linux
mount /dev/cdrom /mnt              # or any other mountpoint
cd /mnt
./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run
reboot

create a shared folder on the host

attache it to the VM in virtual box settings / shared folder

download virtual box + the extension pack

put it in the shared folder

start the VM

download guest addiotion iso
http://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/



-get install -y VirtualBox-4.3-4.3.22_98236_el6-1.x86_64.rpm --print-uris > dependencies
